---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article>
    <h1>Research</h1>

    <h2>Publications in Peer&#8209;Reviewed Journals</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Levine, S., <strong>Hsieh, H.</strong>, Southerton, E., & Silverman, R.
        (2023). <a
